```
BankConsoleApp/                    # Root of the repository
├── .github/                       # GitHub-specific configs
│   └── workflows/                 # CI/CD pipelines
│       └── java-ci.yml           # GitHub Actions for build & test
├── docs/                          # Project documentation
│   └── architecture.md            # High‑level architecture doc
├── src/                           # Source code
│   └── main/                      # Main application code
│       └── java/                  # Java packages
│           └── com/bankapp/       # Base package
│               ├── model/         # Data models (Account, AccountType)
│               ├── dao/           # Data access objects (interfaces & file DAO)
│               ├── service/       # Business logic layer
│               ├── util/          # Utility classes (validation)
│               └── ui/            # Console UI launcher & menu
│   └── test/                      # Unit and integration tests
│       └── java/                  # Mirror of main/java for test packages
│           └── com/bankapp/       # Tests for each layer
│               ├── model/         # Model tests
│               ├── dao/           # DAO tests
│               └── service/       # Service tests
├── accounts.dat                   # Serialized data (gitignored usually)
├── .gitignore                     # Files and folders to ignore
├── LICENSE                        # MIT License text
├── README.md                      # Project overview and quickstart
├── build.gradle or pom.xml        # Build configuration (Gradle or Maven)
└── CONTRIBUTING.md                # Guidelines for contributors
```
